        "action": "Require all schools to let pupils wear their own clothes on Monday and Friday",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I urge the Government to require all schools to let pupils wear their own clothes on Monday and Friday, as I believe having to wear a uniform all week is uncomfortable and annoying for students. I believe this could make students happier and put more effort into their work.",
